Sat Jun 13 10:00:00 UTC 2026 - Travis Post <post.travis@gmail.com> - 0.2.3

- Fixed: Release workflow gates GitHub Release promotion on successful OBS source upload, rebuild trigger, and completed OBS builds (`wait-obs-builds` job).
- Added: `scripts/obs-wait-for-builds.sh` polls OBS build results for repositories configured in `OBS_WAIT_REPOSITORIES`.

